---

<section
  class="px-6 md:px-12 py-20 bg-surface-container-lowest border-y border-outline-variant/10"
  id="identity"
>
  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start"
  >
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-12">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h2
          class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-primary tracking-tighter uppercase"
        >
          &gt; Profile_Identity
        </h2>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-mono text-xs opacity-60">
          KERNEL_MODE // SYSTEM_ARCHITECT.DAT
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3
            class="text-primary-container font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-primary-container/20 pb-2"
          >
            Core_Directives
          </h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Engineer focused on the skeletal structures of the digital world.
            Building invisible yet indestructible systems.
          </p>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Digital brutalism: stripping away the unnecessary until only the core
            functional logic remains.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3
            class="text-primary-container font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-primary-container/20 pb-2"
          >
            Technical_Specs
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 font-mono text-[11px] text-on-surface">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-container"></span>
              <span>EXPERIENCE: 8.4 YEARS_UPTIME</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-container"></span>
              <span>CORE_STACK: GO, RUST, K8S, GRPC</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-container"></span>
              <span>SPECIALIZATION: DISTRIBUTED SYSTEMS</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-container"></span>
              <span>LOCALIZATION: BERLIN // UTC+1</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-surface p-6 border border-outline-variant/20 relative overflow-hidden group"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 font-mono text-[8px] text-primary-container opacity-30"
        >
          ENCRYPTED_DATA_PACKET
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-on-surface-variant italic text-sm font-light leading-relaxed"
        >
          "I approach architecture as a form of digital
          brutalism&mdash;optimizing for the milliseconds that matter and the
          uptime that is non-negotiable."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative group">
      <div
        class="absolute -inset-4 border border-primary-container/20 group-hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all duration-500"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-full aspect-square bg-surface border border-outline-variant/40 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          alt="Cybernetic aesthetic"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-50 contrast-150"
          src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB6Pf5M2zF5mYEGHj-ddNXruVOQn0tAoKEir614wUTgW53CNaGLsovSS1K1Ww6VOU_oD18RtLumJOgufxwvEAn-_eIhYxpCl7y_DcjpJpUc5U92Y0s60bqqkec5iFGOCkgJ68ZmnGT69CvMhWmD9-E-mGc9IRcGmA9JAvoghxkhFbo3Gx-HIekbCJ5bhOA7RurmoKoIY9vouFe_S2hwugNY-TYsRPP1gASFHAMoal7BZODxjb-WJDpTSW0qDcCgb1zr_w69e5SbZP8"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface to-transparent"
        ></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
          <div
            class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-primary-container pb-2 mb-2"
          >
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-primary-container"
              >SCANNING IDENTITY...</span
            >
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-primary-container"
              >98.4% MATCH</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-1">
            <div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-primary-container"></div>
            <div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-primary-container"></div>
            <div class="h-1 flex-1 bg-primary-container"></div>
            <div class="h-1 w-12 bg-outline-variant"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
